<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Reformation" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Reformation,</orth> 1) amendment of manners and sentiments: <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.879" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 879</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.237" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 237</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 1.1.33" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 I, 1, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.3.19" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 3, 19</bibl>.<lb />2) redress of abuses: <cit><quote>your captain is brave and vows r.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.2.70" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 2, 70</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>which r. must be sudden too,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.20" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 3, 20</bibl></cit>.
